Notes
Footnotes

Sources are inconclusive regarding the total amount of Allied shipping sunk. Sources vary between  and .31323334 Sometime sources also speak of 17 war-patrols. L&lt;U+00FC&gt;th aborted two patrols on U-43 prematurely after leaving harbour because of oil leakage.35
The German Reichsmarine was renamed to Kriegsmarine on 1 June 1935.

